Here is the basic pattern. Inventory objects are just children of the player. I'm not really sure what &quot;remove an object&quot; means to you, so I just wrote this to move the object to a room called &quot;Limbo&quot;. But you should be able to adapt this for whatever you want.

[code:25r2oq4f]foreach (child, GetDirectChildren(player)) {
      MoveObject(child, Limbo)
}[/code:25r2oq4f]

